new SafeDivide:
    @ >> arr.
    (arr[0] / arr[1]).
..

new Process:
    @ >> num.
    (100 & num) >> SafeDivide >> catch:
        @ >> err.
        "Recovered from zero division" >> Display.
        -1 >> Return.
    ..
..

[10, 5, 0, 2, 0, 1] >> Map:
    @ >> Process >> Return.
.. >> results.

"Results with default fallback:" >> Display.
results >> Display.
